      "type": "p",
      "text": "Academic Affairs supports NYU Shanghai’s community of scholars, its shared ideals, and core values. Together with the University’s Deans, Area Heads, and Directors, Academic Affairs provides opportunities, infrastructure, and resources to encourage and enable faculty and students to meet the rigorous demands of an NYU Shanghai education and pursue their finest work."
    },
