      "type": "p",
      "text": "Academic Affairs' main responsibilities include academic advising, academic skills building, and academic support for students, governance of academic policies and processes, supporting curricular innovation and teaching excellence, and developing learning opportunities for students inside and outside of the classroom as well as within the NYU Global Network."
